### Third-Party Components and Licensing

This project makes use of @ffmpeg/ffmpeg (https://github.com/ffmpegwasm/ffmpeg.wasm), 
a WebAssembly-based wrapper for FFmpeg. 

FFmpeg itself is licensed under either:
- GPLv3 (https://www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl-3.0.html), or
- LGPLv3 (https://www.gnu.org/licenses/lgpl-3.0.html), depending on the build.

The use of FFmpeg in this project adheres to the license provided by the WebAssembly distribution. 
No modifications have been made to FFmpeg.

To comply with FFmpeg licensing:
1. A copy of the FFmpeg source code is available at https://ffmpeg.org/.
2. FFmpegâ€™s full license text is included in its source code.

This project is provided as open-source software. Donations are accepted voluntarily to support development and hosting.
